[Script for Search and Replace]

This script converts the string to unicode format. To be used with
the Apply Script function in the Binary Mode dialog for the Search
&/or Replace string fields.

The final search/replace using the transformed string can be
Binary mode. Alternatively, use the transformed string in the main
Search and Replace dialog but use Regular Expression Mode.

[Search /ix]
?
[Replace]
\\0x00%1
[End of Search and Replace Script]
